data.text: I pretty much believe I am up to date despite all that. When I started reading newspaper 3 weeks ago, I found that I already know everything by the time i read it. I dont know things i dont have to know e.g the correct name of the radio DJ who failed to protect Nurul Izzah.

I still don't have TV. I watch shows selected based on my viewing habits on Netflix and I should add that, I only listen to my own playlists on Spotify in my car. I got my news from Twitter, Feeds and friends.

Point is, the leaders from the new Msian govt should just stick with BFM for the time being. I am sure it will take a very long time before you can cure other Msian radios and TVs of its "membodohkan rakyat" disease.
